                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The mudwretch spews a 20-foot line of pressurized mud that deals [[/r 2d10 #bludgeoning]]{2d10 bludgeoning damage} (<span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-dc=\"18\" data-pf2-traits=\"conjuration,primal,damaging-effect\" data-pf2-label=\"Spew Mud DC\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">basic Reflex</span> save). On a critical failure, a creature also takes a -10-foot status penalty to its Speeds for 1 round.</p>\n<p>The mudwretch can't Spew Mud again for [[/br 1d4 #rounds]]{1d4 rounds}.</p>"
